===Verb===
{{en-verb|plucks|plucking|'''[[plucked]]''' ''or obsolete'', '''[[pluckt]]'''}}

# {{transitive}} To [[pull]] something [[sharp]]ly; to pull something out
#: ''She '''plucked''' the phone from her bag and phoned her friend.''
# {{cattag|transitive|music}} To gently play a single [[string]], e.g. on a [[guitar]], [[violin]], etc.
#: ''Whereas a [[piano]] strikes the string, a [[harpsichord]] '''plucks''' it.''
# To [[remove]] [[feather]]s from a [[bird]].

